if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都好嘅坦白，佢就話搵到更鍾意嘅人(通常都係新鮮刺激JA)<br />\n但你仲對佢有嘢，做乜柒朋友？等佢俾條仔飛咗，而你又放低咗搵到新女朋友咪同佢講做朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:01:56.000Z","msg":"我都多謝佢坦白同我講 我都明白成世人流流<br />\n點都會有熱情減退嘅時候 只不過無估到我地捱唔過去"},{"pid":"b579218688752171e1c61c1823719d8a4697297f","tid":1396584,"uid":40979,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0a55bb07e5507bc058bbe74e18bf1cf0209f4b09","tid":1396584,"uid":44827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9744df90a96d58f57c50cae756df19b3e36bdc1a","tid":1396584,"uid":40979,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:59:30.000Z","msg":"只係唔想就咁無咗個曾經最重要嘅人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d71928702d038ee5aef0133be6a951a6055f89","tid":1396584,"uid":255036,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:04:52.000Z","msg":"咪制 分手後做朋友<br />\n如果其中一方仲有感覺<br />\n好容易變左做兵<br />\n放過自己 咁落去好易迷失自己"},{"pid":"b07717c180c4e3bc2dfe5fda12306d61a598989f","tid":1396584,"uid":278377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45e8d892787602c9279a1e83c99fce36625f8145","tid":1396584,"uid":44827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:50:46.000Z","msg":"由大學到出嚟做野拍拖就6年 <br />\n一齊住一齊長大 每日幾乎係朝夕相對<br />\n上個星期佢同我講 佢心入面有更鍾意嘅人<br />\n我雖然撕心裂肺 但都好希望佢過得好<br />\n所以我就同佢講分手 還佢自由<br />\n<br />\n我地都約定要做好朋友 <br />\n我原本以為自己可以接受呢個轉變<br />\n但我望到咩都會諗起呢個人<br />\n要好用力壓住自己見佢msg佢嘅衝動<br />\n心入面仲有一絲佢會回心轉意嘅希望<br />\n<br />\n我唔想人生無咗呢個人 即使係朋友關係<br />\n但佢嘅每字每句都會令我心情大起大落<br />\n究竟呢個係咪不可能任務"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:09:13.000Z","msg":"每任都做到朋友/ buddy"},{"pid":"be5da3220813eb58b48bb2deff2ad7c2d245e59e","tid":1396584,"uid":249347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係天方夜譚既，我同初戀而家都係再見亦是朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年分左手一年，佢外國讀書放暑期返黎香港，問我有冇興趣一齊出黎食過飯，咁就變左每年我地都見面一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n慢慢發展到而家咩都會傾下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，大家分別拍拖時，會比另一半既相比大家過目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最緊要大家互相都放低左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b5781d73520c17c59bbc2eba66558bd1584a2ea","tid":1396584,"uid":44827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b579218688752171e1c61c1823719d8a4697297f","tid":1396584,"uid":40979,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0a55bb07e5507bc058bbe74e18bf1cf0209f4b09","tid":1396584,"uid":44827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9744df90a96d58f57c50cae756df19b3e36bdc1a","tid":1396584,"uid":40979,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:59:30.000Z","msg":"只係唔想就咁無咗個曾經最重要嘅人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:11:15.000Z","msg":"一齊生活同互相依靠咗咁耐<br />\n其實大家已經當對方係屋企人<br />\n只係因為愛情唔係淨係睇你對佢好唔好咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b1a1054ac50fdb860ae2d533a745618148b75e","tid":1396584,"uid":44827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9d71928702d038ee5aef0133be6a951a6055f89","tid":1396584,"uid":255036,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:04:5